VCLASS_ERROR = "Class "+VCLASSCOD+" : " + "Initialization error"
Return

Funprog GETACTCONTRACT(VREFNUM)
Value Char VREFNUM
Local Char VCTRNUM(GLONHRCTR)
Local File EMPLOCTR [CTR8]
Filter [CTR8] Where REFNUM = VREFNUM and XITDAT = [00/00/00]
Read [CTR8]CTR0 First
If fstat = [V]CST_AOK
  VCTRNUM = [F:CTR8]CTRNUM
Endif
End VCTRNUM

